## Task Solution:

**1. Analyze and Describe the Main Target Image:**

*   **Count & Layers:** The structure is composed of **17 blocks** and has **3 layers** at its highest point.
*   **Spatial Relationships:**
    *   **Base Layer:** The base layer consists of four red arch blocks arranged linearly from left to right, forming two sets of arches with a small gap in between.
    *   **Second Layer (Left Section):** On the left set of arches (first two arches), there are two green rectangular blocks placed side-by-side, spanning across both arches.
    *   **Second Layer (Right Section):** On the right set of arches (last two arches), there is one yellow semi-circle block placed on the left arch and one yellow rectangular block placed on the right arch.
    *   **Third Layer (Left Section):** On top of the green rectangular blocks (left section), there is a blue cube on the left and a yellow rectangular block on the right.
    *   **Third Layer (Right Section):** On top of the yellow semi-circle block (left arch of right set), there is a vertical green rectangular block. On top of the yellow rectangular block (right arch of right set), there are two vertical yellow rectangular blocks placed side by side.
    *   **Top Layer (Right Section):** On top of the vertical green rectangular block, there is an orange cube. On top of the two vertical yellow rectangular blocks, there is a red house-roof block on the left and an orange house-roof block on the right.
    *   There is one additional green rectangular block placed at the far right end on the base layer, next to the rightmost arch.

**2. Select the Required Blocks from the Dictionary:**

*   **Needed Blocks and Indices:**
    *   Red Arch (base layer): Block 1 (x4)
    *   Green Rectangular (horizontal, layer 2 left): Block 4 (x2)
    *   Yellow Semi-circle (layer 2 right): Block 12 (x1)
    *   Yellow Rectangular (horizontal, layer 2 right): Block 9 (x1)
    *   Blue Cube (layer 3 left): Block 3 (x1)
    *   Yellow Rectangular (horizontal, layer 3 left): Block 9 (x1)
    *   Green Rectangular (vertical, layer 3 right): Block 8 (x1)
    *   Yellow Rectangular (vertical, layer 3 right): Block 11 (x2)
    *   Orange Cube (top right): Block 5 (x1)
    *   Red House-roof (top right): Block 15 (x1)
    *   Orange House-roof (top right): Block 16 (x1)
    *   Green Rectangular (horizontal, base layer right end): Block 4 (x1)

*   **List of Block Indices (in order of appearance in the structure, roughly bottom to top, left to right):** 1, 1, 1, 1, 4, 4, 12, 9, 3, 9, 8, 11, 11, 5, 15, 16, 4
